        <h1>My Go To Starbucks Order</h1>
        <p>I have tried a lot of different Starbucks orders 
            but this is by far my favorite combination that 
            I have found. </p>

        <h2>What to Order for a Drink</h2>
        <p>I always order the following as such; Could I please 
            get a <b><abbr title="Medium sized drink">Grande</abbr> 
            White Mocha with an extra shot of espresso with 
            oat milk and no whipped cream.</b></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Grande</li>
            <li>White Mocha</li>
            <li>Extra Shot</li>
            <li>Oat Milk</li>
            <li>No Whipped Cream</li>
        </ol>

        <h3>What to order for food</h3>
        <p>The best food option in my opinion is the <b>Sausage
            Cheddar and Egg breakfast sandwich.</b></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Sausage, Cheddar and Egg Sandwich</li>
        </ol>
        <p>For more ordering options visit <a 
            href="https://www.starbucks.com">Starbucks Homepage</a></p>

